WEBVTT

00:00:00.199 --> 00:00:03.230
Good morning family, praise the Lord!

00:00:03.240 --> 00:00:05.110
I'm glad you all joined me again today

00:00:05.120 --> 00:00:07.590
to pray. We have a lot

00:00:07.600 --> 00:00:09.589
of work to do actually, but I just want

00:00:09.599 --> 00:00:12.470
to give you all a testimony real quick

00:00:12.480 --> 00:00:15.350
about a lady

00:00:15.350 --> 00:00:15.360
who

00:00:15.360 --> 00:00:17.070
reached out to us for prayer. She said she

00:00:17.080 --> 00:00:19.150
broke her hip and four ribs and was in a lot of pain. I prayed for her on

00:00:19.160 --> 00:00:21.950
this video right here, and she

00:00:30.880 --> 00:00:34.310
contacted us

00:00:34.320 --> 00:00:36.590
and told us, 'When you were

00:00:36.600 --> 00:00:39.510
praying and believing for my healing, I

00:00:39.520 --> 00:00:41.150
just want to let you know the Lord

00:00:41.160 --> 00:00:44.549
healed me.'I want to give

00:00:44.559 --> 00:00:46.869
all the glory, honor, and praise to the

00:00:46.879 --> 00:00:50.029
Lord Jesus Christ. He is the healer, and He

00:00:50.029 --> 00:00:50.039
is

00:00:50.039 --> 00:00:53.229
healing the sick, the same yesterday,

00:00:53.239 --> 00:00:56.069
today, and forever. He is a good God and He is a

00:00:56.079 --> 00:00:58.029
healer. That's why I have

00:00:58.039 --> 00:01:00.430
this shirt here; I want this to stand

00:01:00.440 --> 00:01:02.590
bold in black and white:

00:01:02.600 --> 00:01:04.429
'Jesus the

00:01:04.429 --> 00:01:04.439
Healer.'He

00:01:04.439 --> 00:01:07.310
is still

00:01:07.320 --> 00:01:10.109
healing the sick today, folks.

00:01:10.119 --> 00:01:12.270
I'm bold

00:01:12.280 --> 00:01:13.950
about it because I've seen it

00:01:13.960 --> 00:01:16.350
time and time again that He's

00:01:16.360 --> 00:01:18.789
doing it.

00:01:18.799 --> 00:01:21.670
We have to take it by faith.

00:01:21.670 --> 00:01:21.680
You've

00:01:21.680 --> 00:01:23.789
got to reach out and grab the hem of His

00:01:23.799 --> 00:01:26.190
garment by faith and call those

00:01:26.200 --> 00:01:28.469
things that be not as though they were.

00:01:28.479 --> 00:01:30.310
I'm excited about that; I just wanted

00:01:30.320 --> 00:01:32.310
to give God praise, a

00:01:32.320 --> 00:01:35.109
testimony, and a shout of glory because He

00:01:35.119 --> 00:01:37.469
is doing miracles through this YouTube

00:01:37.479 --> 00:01:39.590
channel. I'm believing for your

00:01:39.600 --> 00:01:41.510
manifestation. There's a

00:01:41.520 --> 00:01:43.830
gentleman named Keith, and

00:01:43.840 --> 00:01:46.870
for his privacy's sake, his last name

00:01:46.880 --> 00:01:50.830
starts with an R. He writes us

00:01:50.830 --> 00:01:50.840
well-written

00:01:50.840 --> 00:01:54.389
letters that

00:01:54.389 --> 00:01:54.399
bless

00:01:54.399 --> 00:01:57.789
me every

00:01:57.799 --> 00:02:00.350
single time.

00:02:00.360 --> 00:02:03.670
He

00:02:03.670 --> 00:02:03.680
is

00:02:03.680 --> 00:02:05.670
just so awesome in the way he talks about

00:02:05.680 --> 00:02:07.510
his family and everything

00:02:07.520 --> 00:02:08.910
he's going through. He's an

00:02:08.920 --> 00:02:11.550
elderly gentleman, but we look forward to

00:02:11.560 --> 00:02:13.670
him writing to us because

00:02:13.680 --> 00:02:15.670
we've kept every single one;

00:02:15.670 --> 00:02:15.680
they

00:02:15.680 --> 00:02:17.190
are

00:02:17.200 --> 00:02:19.390
very precious to us. He is

00:02:19.400 --> 00:02:21.949
asking for his children to come home

00:02:21.959 --> 00:02:23.869
to the Lord. They are very liberal and

00:02:23.879 --> 00:02:28.030
need a touch, so I'm going

00:02:28.040 --> 00:02:30.790
to believe God with him today.

00:02:34.480 --> 00:02:37.470
I felt

00:02:37.480 --> 00:02:40.910
the cry for the children to come

00:02:40.920 --> 00:02:44.030
home in that letter, and it really moved me today

00:02:44.040 --> 00:02:47.190
when I got it.

00:02:47.200 --> 00:02:49.630
The Lord was showing me there are so

00:02:49.640 --> 00:02:52.350
many of you that have children who are

00:02:52.360 --> 00:02:56.630
wayward.

00:02:56.640 --> 00:02:58.710
You feel like you're at the

00:02:58.720 --> 00:03:00.830
end of your rope sometimes,

00:03:00.830 --> 00:03:00.840
feeling

00:03:00.840 --> 00:03:03.030
that there's no hope because

00:03:03.030 --> 00:03:03.040
they are

00:03:03.040 --> 00:03:04.750
so lost

00:03:04.760 --> 00:03:06.509
and

00:03:06.519 --> 00:03:08.070
it

00:03:08.080 --> 00:03:10.830
seems so far out there. When you're

00:03:10.840 --> 00:03:13.509
at the end of the rope, Jesus has grabbed

00:03:13.509 --> 00:03:13.519
onto

00:03:13.519 --> 00:03:15.110
the rope with

00:03:15.120 --> 00:03:18.190
you. When all else is

00:03:18.190 --> 00:03:18.200
done,

00:03:18.200 --> 00:03:20.550
stand therefore. I just want to

00:03:20.560 --> 00:03:24.430
encourage every single one of you: do not

00:03:24.440 --> 00:03:27.910
give up on your unsaved loved ones.

00:03:27.920 --> 00:03:31.630
When I had my

00:03:31.630 --> 00:03:31.640
visitation

00:03:31.640 --> 00:03:33.949
almost

00:03:33.959 --> 00:03:36.190
over two weeks ago,

00:03:36.190 --> 00:03:36.200
the Lord

00:03:36.200 --> 00:03:40.670
told me, 'You must

00:03:40.680 --> 00:03:43.110
pray for the blinders to come off their

00:03:43.120 --> 00:03:45.670
eyes and that the eyes of their

00:03:45.680 --> 00:03:47.589
understanding would be

00:03:47.589 --> 00:03:47.599
enlightened.'Satan

00:03:47.599 --> 00:03:50.949
blinds the eyes of the

00:03:50.959 --> 00:03:54.110
unbeliever and causes it so that they

00:03:54.120 --> 00:03:57.030
can't see the light of the truth.

00:03:57.040 --> 00:03:59.069
The Bible says

00:03:59.069 --> 00:03:59.079
to

00:03:59.079 --> 00:04:00.830
train up a child in the way they should

00:04:00.840 --> 00:04:02.630
go, and when they get older, they will not

00:04:02.640 --> 00:04:04.990
depart from it. Regardless, even if

00:04:05.000 --> 00:04:06.509
they're wayward, they're going to come

00:04:06.519 --> 00:04:08.830
back because those seeds of truth are

00:04:08.840 --> 00:04:12.270
planted inside of them. You may say,

00:04:12.280 --> 00:04:13.830
'I never trained them up in the way

00:04:13.840 --> 00:04:17.789
they should go,'but it doesn't matter; God's

00:04:17.799 --> 00:04:20.270
merciful, and I believe we can turn them

00:04:20.280 --> 00:04:23.790
around by prayer. The same Jesus Christ

00:04:23.800 --> 00:04:25.990
of Nazareth that was raised 2,000 years

00:04:26.000 --> 00:04:28.350
ago from the dead dwells on the inside

00:04:28.360 --> 00:04:31.430
of you. Do you believe it? Do you

00:04:31.440 --> 00:04:33.270
believe you have power and authority

00:04:33.280 --> 00:04:35.590
over the devil? You might say, 'I believe

00:04:35.600 --> 00:04:37.310
you do, Brother

00:04:37.310 --> 00:04:37.320
Brandon,'but

00:04:37.320 --> 00:04:39.710
do you

00:04:39.720 --> 00:04:41.670
believe you do? He's no respecter of

00:04:41.680 --> 00:04:43.950
persons; the same Jesus that lives

00:04:43.960 --> 00:04:46.310
inside of me lives inside of you.

00:04:46.320 --> 00:04:48.150
I'm telling you, we have power and

00:04:48.160 --> 00:04:49.550
authority over the devil because the

00:04:49.560 --> 00:04:52.430
Bible tells us we do, so we have to use

00:04:52.430 --> 00:04:52.440
it

00:04:52.440 --> 00:04:54.270
today.

00:04:54.280 --> 00:04:56.390
We cannot just sit

00:04:56.400 --> 00:04:59.070
there and pray a weak, anemic prayer.

00:05:06.960 --> 00:05:09.870
I believe it's time we get bold about

00:05:09.880 --> 00:05:12.350
our faith and know that all things are

00:05:12.360 --> 00:05:15.390
possible to him who believes. Greater

00:05:15.400 --> 00:05:18.309
is He that is in you

00:05:18.319 --> 00:05:20.070
than he that is in the world.

00:05:22.309 --> 00:05:22.319
Let's

00:05:23.800 --> 00:05:25.710
get started and pray for the

00:05:25.710 --> 00:05:25.720
wayward

00:05:25.720 --> 00:05:27.749
children. I'm using

00:05:27.759 --> 00:05:30.790
Keith R's children as a point of contact

00:05:30.800 --> 00:05:32.629
for every single one of you.

00:05:32.639 --> 00:05:35.270
When we pray for our

00:05:35.280 --> 00:05:38.029
brother and take our needs off of

00:05:40.670 --> 00:05:40.680
ourselves,

00:05:42.960 --> 00:05:44.430
there's power in prayer.

00:05:47.070 --> 00:05:47.080
You

00:05:49.919 --> 00:05:51.469
have

00:05:53.120 --> 00:05:55.790
to take your eyes off the problem

00:05:58.080 --> 00:05:59.390
and look into

00:05:59.390 --> 00:05:59.400
Jesus'face

00:05:59.400 --> 00:06:02.670
because He's the answer.

00:06:12.880 --> 00:06:15.270
He has America,

00:06:15.280 --> 00:06:17.390
Australia, Canada, and

00:06:17.390 --> 00:06:17.400
Asia—He

00:06:17.400 --> 00:06:19.670
has all of it, folks. I believe with

00:06:19.680 --> 00:06:22.350
all my heart we will see

00:06:22.360 --> 00:06:24.710
the greatest outpouring of

00:06:24.720 --> 00:06:27.029
the Spirit of God this world has

00:06:27.039 --> 00:06:29.550
seen yet, and we're going to see a

00:06:29.550 --> 00:06:29.560
major

00:06:29.560 --> 00:06:32.189
move of His presence in these last

00:06:32.199 --> 00:06:36.830
days. Father, we just

00:06:36.840 --> 00:06:39.990
thank You for Keith R's children and

00:06:40.000 --> 00:06:42.110
we call all these children in right now

00:06:42.120 --> 00:06:43.589
in the name of Jesus. We're going to take

00:06:43.599 --> 00:06:47.430
communion over it and we say, 'Satan, take

00:06:47.440 --> 00:06:49.990
your hands off of our

00:06:50.000 --> 00:06:53.710
children! Get your hands off of their

00:06:53.710 --> 00:06:53.720
eyes!'I

00:06:53.720 --> 00:06:56.990
thank You, Lord, that You said

00:06:57.000 --> 00:06:59.589
if we call those

00:06:59.599 --> 00:07:01.790
things that be not as though they were,

00:07:01.800 --> 00:07:05.510
we say they are saved, they are

00:07:05.520 --> 00:07:08.270
filled with the Holy Ghost, and they are on

00:07:08.280 --> 00:07:10.990
fire for Jesus. They are no longer

00:07:11.000 --> 00:07:13.629
wayward, but they are coming

00:07:13.639 --> 00:07:17.070
home. I thank You, Lord, that

00:07:17.080 --> 00:07:20.830
this is the time for them to get

00:07:20.840 --> 00:07:24.150
radically born again. Father, I thank

00:07:24.160 --> 00:07:27.189
You that You will not allow

00:07:27.199 --> 00:07:30.189
any of our children to go to hell. We

00:07:30.199 --> 00:07:35.309
stand in that gap

00:07:35.319 --> 00:07:38.390
interceding for them.

00:07:38.400 --> 00:07:41.350
Angels, I thank You that

00:07:41.360 --> 00:07:44.110
You're going on behalf of each and every

00:07:44.110 --> 00:07:44.120
person

00:07:44.120 --> 00:07:45.950
that

00:07:45.950 --> 00:07:45.960
has

00:07:45.960 --> 00:07:48.710
wayward children, and we call forth the

00:07:48.720 --> 00:07:50.990
mighty hand of the Lord to move

00:07:51.000 --> 00:07:53.390
right now.

00:07:53.400 --> 00:07:57.909
We call forth results:

00:08:00.000 --> 00:08:01.670
first the blade, then the ear, then the

00:08:01.680 --> 00:08:04.390
full manifestation. It's time

00:08:04.400 --> 00:08:07.589
for a great acceleration when it comes

00:08:07.599 --> 00:08:11.350
to wayward children

00:08:11.350 --> 00:08:11.360
coming

00:08:11.360 --> 00:08:14.070
home.

00:08:14.080 --> 00:08:16.110
Every person represented

00:08:16.120 --> 00:08:18.309
here today who has wayward children,

00:08:18.319 --> 00:08:21.390
we say they

00:08:21.400 --> 00:08:24.110
are not wayward anymore. They are saved, filled with the Holy

00:08:24.120 --> 00:08:26.830
Ghost, and on fire for You, Lord.

00:08:32.519 --> 00:08:35.269
We take

00:08:35.279 --> 00:08:38.110
authority over those blinders

00:08:38.110 --> 00:08:38.120
and

00:08:38.120 --> 00:08:41.550
say that

00:08:41.560 --> 00:08:43.509
the eyes of their understanding would be

00:08:43.519 --> 00:08:46.509
enlightened.

00:08:46.519 --> 00:08:49.790
I call them in, and I call the Lord

00:08:49.800 --> 00:08:51.829
of the harvest to bring in those

00:08:51.839 --> 00:08:53.829
children, relatives,

00:08:53.839 --> 00:08:56.470
husbands, or

00:08:56.480 --> 00:09:00.790
wayward wives. No more, Satan!

00:09:00.800 --> 00:09:03.630
You will not have our loved ones.

00:09:03.640 --> 00:09:06.269
We call the hardness of their

00:09:06.269 --> 00:09:06.279
hearts

00:09:06.279 --> 00:09:09.509
to be pliable and soft to the

00:09:09.519 --> 00:09:12.350
gospel.

00:09:17.279 --> 00:09:18.990
We thank You, Lord, that they're calling

00:09:19.000 --> 00:09:21.710
today and saying, 'Mom, Dad,

00:09:21.720 --> 00:09:24.910
I am coming home. I want to be

00:09:24.920 --> 00:09:28.310
born again. I see the error in my ways

00:09:28.320 --> 00:09:30.430
and I know I've been wrong and I've been

00:09:30.430 --> 00:09:30.440
wayward

00:09:30.440 --> 00:09:33.269
and today I want to turn around

00:09:33.279 --> 00:09:35.949
and

00:09:35.949 --> 00:09:35.959
repent.'I

00:09:35.959 --> 00:09:39.150
stand in agreement with every

00:09:39.160 --> 00:09:41.470
single one of you.

00:09:43.600 --> 00:09:46.670
Father, we take communion over

00:09:46.680 --> 00:09:49.069
it. You're

00:09:52.000 --> 00:09:55.069
a healer and a deliverer,

00:09:55.079 --> 00:09:57.110
and You will bring

00:09:57.120 --> 00:09:58.790
those

00:09:58.800 --> 00:10:00.870
wayward family members home because

00:10:00.880 --> 00:10:02.870
their eyes are open and

00:10:02.880 --> 00:10:04.590
they know the error in

00:10:04.600 --> 00:10:06.509
their ways. They don't want to

00:10:06.519 --> 00:10:09.470
go to hell. May they have an inward

00:10:09.480 --> 00:10:11.470
shaking

00:10:11.480 --> 00:10:13.590
experience with the Holy Spirit to wake

00:10:13.600 --> 00:10:14.710
them up in the middle of the night. I

00:10:14.710 --> 00:10:14.720
thank You,

00:10:14.720 --> 00:10:18.030
Lord, for

00:10:18.030 --> 00:10:18.040
angelic

00:10:18.040 --> 00:10:20.150
visitations and

00:10:20.160 --> 00:10:23.750
manifestations of angelic beings.

00:10:27.640 --> 00:10:29.350
I thank You, Lord, that as

00:10:29.360 --> 00:10:31.949
we take this body, we're believing by

00:10:31.959 --> 00:10:33.910
faith

00:10:33.920 --> 00:10:35.389
that

00:10:35.399 --> 00:10:37.550
You're bringing all of our kids home.

00:10:37.560 --> 00:10:39.150
We take

00:10:39.160 --> 00:10:40.629
it by faith that we're healed and whole.

00:10:40.639 --> 00:10:43.069
No viruses will come nigh

00:10:43.079 --> 00:10:46.030
us this winter—no flu, no pestilence,

00:10:46.040 --> 00:10:49.030
no plagues, no nothing comes nigh us, Father.

00:10:49.040 --> 00:10:51.629
We walk in divine

00:10:51.639 --> 00:10:54.990
health—no

00:10:55.000 --> 00:10:58.750
respiratory issues, colds, or sinus

00:10:58.760 --> 00:11:00.470
infections.

00:11:03.120 --> 00:11:05.509
For You were wounded for

00:11:05.519 --> 00:11:07.990
our transgressions, You were bruised for

00:11:08.000 --> 00:11:10.230
our iniquities, the chastisement of our

00:11:10.240 --> 00:11:13.150
peace was upon You, and with Your stripes

00:11:13.160 --> 00:11:15.470
we are healed. I call forth new

00:11:15.480 --> 00:11:18.590
hearts, even for Sherry.

00:11:18.600 --> 00:11:21.350
I thank You, Lord, for a creative

00:11:21.360 --> 00:11:23.509
miracle in Sherry's heart even with that

00:11:23.519 --> 00:11:25.750
pacemaker. We speak

00:11:25.750 --> 00:11:25.760
to that

00:11:25.760 --> 00:11:28.190
heart:

00:11:28.200 --> 00:11:30.910
be

00:11:30.920 --> 00:11:33.230
healed in the name of Jesus! Sherry, from

00:11:33.240 --> 00:11:34.910
the top of your head to the souls of

00:11:34.920 --> 00:11:37.870
your feet, no more of this fear and

00:11:37.880 --> 00:11:40.670
torment over you anymore. We

00:11:40.670 --> 00:11:40.680
take

00:11:40.680 --> 00:11:42.629
authority over that

00:11:42.639 --> 00:11:44.870
demonic spirit

00:11:44.880 --> 00:11:46.629
whispering in your ear and

00:11:46.639 --> 00:11:48.590
command it to go now!

00:11:48.600 --> 00:11:51.949
The Lord says to fill your mind

00:11:51.959 --> 00:11:54.870
and spirit with His Word

00:12:08.600 --> 00:12:10.190
and meditate on

00:12:10.200 --> 00:12:12.949
it like you

00:12:12.949 --> 00:12:12.959
would take medicine.

00:12:12.959 --> 00:12:15.590
Meditate on His Word until it becomes

00:12:15.590 --> 00:12:15.600
Rhema

00:12:15.600 --> 00:12:18.430
in your spirit and the breakthrough

00:12:18.440 --> 00:12:21.150
is there. The heart is related to

00:12:21.160 --> 00:12:24.310
fear

00:12:24.310 --> 00:12:24.320
and

00:12:24.320 --> 00:12:26.670
meditation on the wrong

00:12:26.670 --> 00:12:26.680
things.

00:12:26.680 --> 00:12:29.350
Meditate on the Word so

00:12:29.350 --> 00:12:29.360
you

00:12:29.360 --> 00:12:31.110
know the truth, and the truth will

00:12:31.120 --> 00:12:33.750
set you free.

00:12:33.760 --> 00:12:36.150
But you've got to get the heart lined up

00:12:36.160 --> 00:12:38.509
with the Word, because the Bible says that

00:12:38.519 --> 00:12:41.550
men's hearts will fail them for fear

00:12:41.560 --> 00:12:43.710
looking at those things

00:12:43.720 --> 00:12:45.910
coming upon the Earth.

00:12:45.920 --> 00:12:47.470
You've

00:12:47.480 --> 00:12:50.230
got to get fear out,

00:12:50.240 --> 00:12:53.629
for fear tolerated is faith contaminated. You've got

00:12:53.629 --> 00:12:53.639
to get the

00:12:53.639 --> 00:12:55.590
Word in to

00:12:55.590 --> 00:12:55.600
transform the

00:12:55.600 --> 00:12:57.829
fear

00:13:05.160 --> 00:13:07.470
you've been meditating on.

00:13:09.760 --> 00:13:12.189
It may take having less time

00:13:12.189 --> 00:13:12.199
on

00:13:12.199 --> 00:13:14.670
social media and

00:13:14.680 --> 00:13:17.550
YouTube, but getting the Word down inside

00:13:17.550 --> 00:13:17.560
is

00:13:17.560 --> 00:13:19.910
more important because

00:13:19.920 --> 00:13:22.389
His words are

00:13:22.399 --> 00:13:25.069
life to those that find them and health

00:13:25.079 --> 00:13:27.470
